author: Ellen Killoran
title: Bob Odenkirk and David Cross Are a Comedic Dream Team in the With Bob & David Trailer
text:
Netflix has released a new trailer for With Bob & David , an upcoming variety sketch show from the former stars of the beloved series Mr. Show . With only weeks until the new series premieres, fans can get a taste of the semi-highbrow humor that Bob Odenkirk and David Cross will bring to the half-hour series. Though the format has some throwback appeal, Cross and Odenkirk bring a very contemporary edge to their skewering of pop culture tropes. Who needs SNL ?
With Bob & David will premiere on Netflix on November 13.
